graph TD
    START([Start: 4 JARs + manifests]) --> EXT[ExtractorAgent<br/>Unpack JARs<br/>Read pega.xml manifests<br/>Build file catalog]
    EXT --> PARSE[RuleParserAgent<br/>Stream XML<br/>Classify by pxObjClass<br/>Write to SQLite catalog]

    PARSE --> HM[HierarchyMapperAgent<br/>Ruleset → Class → Property<br/>Inheritance chain<br/>Access roles]
    PARSE --> FA[FlowAnalyzerAgent<br/>Case Types → Stages → Steps<br/>Flow shapes & transitions<br/>Decision tables/trees]
    PARSE --> UI[UIRendererAgent<br/>Sections & Harnesses<br/>Layout reconstruction<br/>→ standalone HTML]

    FA --> TX[TaskExtractorAgent<br/>Assignments & Routers<br/>SLAs & Escalations<br/>Task generation ledger]

    HM --> SYN[DocSynthesizerAgent<br/>Program Documentation<br/>Hierarchy + Flows +<br/>Tasks + UI Index]
    TX --> SYN
    UI --> SYN

    SYN --> OUT([Outputs:<br/>program_doc.md<br/>program_doc.html<br/>ui/*.html<br/>catalog.sqlite])

    classDef agent fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#0a1929,color:#fff
    classDef io fill:#d4a017,stroke:#8b6914,color:#000
    class EXT,PARSE,HM,FA,UI,TX,SYN agent
    class START,OUT io
